Reftele, som v. kommin. i Södra Möckleby, som v. pastor i Hulter-6.t)ad’, Väckiellsiånig, Hinnieiryd isiamit Äilg-hult, kommin. i Algutsboda ised. 42.
translated: Dahlborg, Nils, clergyman, Algutsboda, born on January 20, 1907 in Ljungby to builder Emil D. and Hildur Buhré. Married in 1940 to Stina Emborg. Children: Nife Olof Gudmund born in 1944, Kerstin Maria born in 1947. He studied at Kalmar in 1927 and obtained his BA in theology from Lund University in 1931. He also completed his theological candidacy and practical examination in 1936 and was ordained as a priest for the Växjö diocese in the same year. He served as an interim pastor in various locations including Köping, Södra Möckleby, Glömminge, Väckelsång, Hakarp, Fors-heda and Reftele. He also served as an assistant pastor in Södra Möckleby and as a pastor in Hultsfred, Väckelsång, Hinneryd and Älghult, and as a clergyman in Algutsboda from 1942.
